Description: ### Install Package
        ```
        pip3 install gappy
        ```
        compatible python version: 3.4+
        
        ### How to use
        
        #### Run with flask
        
        Example:
        
        ```
        import gappy
        from flask import Flask
        from flask import request
        
        TOKEN = '<your token>'
        
        bot = gappy.Bot(TOKEN)
        app = Flask(__name__)
        
        
        @app.route('/', methods=['POST'])
        def parse_request():
            msg = request.form
            content_type = msg['type']
            chat_id = msg['chat_id']
            data = msg['data']
            bot.send_text(chat_id, data)
            return 'OK'
        
        
        if __name__ == '__main__':
            app.run()
        ```
        
